## Subscribe to Execution Events

**Send this message after connecting:**
```json
{
  "type": "subscribe",
  "payload": {
    "execution_id": "ce5a9175-1691-4f58-84f2-c814768e68fa"
  }
}
```

### Response
```json
{
  "type": "subscribed",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "ce5a9175-1691-4f58-84f2-c814768e68fa"
  }
}
```

You'll then receive all events for that specific execution.

## Subscribe to Workflow Events

**Send this message after connecting:**
```json
{
  "type": "subscribe",
  "payload": {
    "workflow_id": "092e689f-a562-4e3e-8c22-160db0126695"
  }
}
```

### Response
```json
{
  "type": "subscribed",
  "data": {
    "workflow_id": "092e689f-a562-4e3e-8c22-160db0126695"
  }
}
```

You'll receive events for all executions of this workflow.

## Unsubscribe from Events

**Send this message after connecting:**
```json
{
  "type": "unsubscribe",
  "payload": {
    "execution_id": "ce5a9175-1691-4f58-84f2-c814768e68fa"
  }
}
```

Or for workflow:
```json
{
  "type": "unsubscribe",
  "payload": {
    "workflow_id": "092e689f-a562-4e3e-8c22-160db0126695"
  }
}
```

## Ping (Keep-Alive)

**Send this message to keep connection alive:**
```json
{
  "type": "ping"
}
```

### Response
```json
{
  "type": "pong"
}
```

## WebSocket Events Reference

### execution.started
Received when a workflow execution begins.
```json
{
  "type": "execution.started",
  "timestamp": "2025-12-21T12:58:21Z",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "ce5a9175-1691-4f58-84f2-c814768e68fa",
    "workflow_id": "092e689f-a562-4e3e-8c22-160db0126695",
    "status": "running",
    "trigger_type": "manual"
  }
}
```

### node.started
Received when a node begins executing.
```json
{
  "type": "node.started",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "...",
    "workflow_id": "...",
    "node_id": "http",
    "node_name": "Fetch Data",
    "node_type": "action.http",
    "status": "running"
  }
}
```

### node.completed
Received when a node finishes successfully.
```json
{
  "type": "node.completed",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "...",
    "node_id": "http",
    "status": "completed",
    "duration_ms": 3302,
    "output_preview": { "status": 200, "ok": true }
  }
}
```

### node.failed
Received when a node fails.
```json
{
  "type": "node.failed",
  "data": {
    "node_id": "http",
    "status": "failed",
    "error": "connection timeout",
    "duration_ms": 30000
  }
}
```

### execution.completed
Received when workflow finishes successfully.
```json
{
  "type": "execution.completed",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "...",
    "status": "completed",
    "duration_ms": 3303,
    "nodes_completed": 2
  }
}
```

### execution.failed
Received when workflow fails.
```json
{
  "type": "execution.failed",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "...",
    "status": "failed",
    "error": "Node 'http' failed: timeout",
    "error_node_id": "http"
  }
}
```

### execution.cancelled
Received when workflow is cancelled.
```json
{
  "type": "execution.cancelled",
  "data": {
    "execution_id": "...",
    "status": "cancelled",
    "cancelled_by": "user"
  }
}
```
